cd Mythic-Art-Explorer
2. Create virtual environment
bash
复制代码
python3 -m venv venv
source venv/bin/activate   # macOS / Linux
venv\Scripts\activate      # Windows
3. Install dependencies
bash
复制代码
pip install -r requirements.txt
4. Run the application
bash
复制代码
streamlit run app.py
Deploy on Streamlit Cloud
Push this project to GitHub.

Go to: https://streamlit.io/cloud

Click "New app".

Select the repository.

Choose:

app.py as the entry file

Python 3.10 or 3.11 environment

Deploy.

Data Source
This project uses the following public dataset:

The Metropolitan Museum of Art Collection API (Open Access)
https://metmuseum.github.io/

All artworks used are Open Access and free for educational use.

